ilot program that will be in use until december 2011 when it will be evaluated for future continuation printer friendly version student affairs the student affairs division is responsible for programs and services that focus on students and their stanford experience while also engaging with faculty staff parents alumni and the community at large copyright 2011 stanford university terms of use copyright complaints report a problem with this site
